RUF015 [*] Prefer `next(*x for x in xs)` over single element slice
 --> RUF015_py315.py:3:1
  |
1 | xs = [[1], [2]]
2 |
3 | [*x for x in xs][0]
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
4 | list(*x for x in xs)[0]
  |
help: Replace with `next(*x for x in xs)`
1 | xs = [[1], [2]]
2 |
  - [*x for x in xs][0]
3 + next(*x for x in xs)
4 | list(*x for x in xs)[0]
note: This is an unsafe fix and may change runtime behavior

